{"tid":872490,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"我地鐵唔見銀包，於是改左首歌","createTime":"2018-10-22T17:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T17:37:14.000Z","uid":113126,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab540655e963d7afc7424b1c8bf78ebda245f10b","tid":872490,"uid":113126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"奧運六子 遇強愈勇(補領證件)<br />\n月台路線<br />\n跌下證件<br />\n各個暗角 拋開天真<br />\n盼望來電慰問<br />\n就如射箭<br />\n補領證件<br />\n鬥快鬥勇補返證件爭取今天<br />\n在企位 能遺下也是注定<br />\n我馬上報警 我高呼替他打氣<br />\n是你嗎 來電又確認記錄<br />\n這次是信件 極焦急理得你<br />\n聲音較高 月台哪邊通訊好<br />\n到了客服這邊搵訊號<br />\n一千也好 只要結果比較好<br />\n我願薄酬求你看倒<br />\n<br />\n啦X N<br />\n<br />\n續秒鐘 留下了作為記認<br />\n心愛是證件 要補領我骨都痹<br />\n別放鬆 為理想也為美夢<br />\n轉眼又揭盅 八點他已收工<br />\n聲音較高 月台哪邊通訊好<br />\n到了客服這邊搵訊號<br />\n一千也好 只要結果比較好<br />\n我願薄酬求你看倒<br />\n<br />\n有冇人今日下午8點地鐵搵倒銀包，我淨係想要返D證。"},{"pid":"a27aa8f77cd09c9809c29f4eaad140a859b9bab8","tid":872490,"uid":200258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"d439ef6dc551cf806c6f597fc26058c499d18dbc","tid":872490,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"即係奧運唔見？"},{"pid":"35420aaef31f4a7e8363e1a9a3af4f0488b79047","tid":872490,"uid":113126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"原曲:<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p3AVKbY0VTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp3AVKbY0VTM&d=nVIhS4%2BOkUQoKi76uSyciC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c2513eb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p3AVKbY0VTM</a>"},{"pid":"302206f0703ee73090670930eaea9c044dc6eb50","tid":872490,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:30:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa7bd9b9bf54614f4cd5497398b093752775d4cf","tid":872490,"uid":113126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d439ef6dc551cf806c6f597fc26058c499d18dbc","tid":872490,"uid":67237,"like":0,"disli